26:48.950 --> 26:51.230
is actually

26:51.230 --> 26:53.410
I can say that is a very,

26:53.410 --> 26:55.230
very, very big...

26:59.810 --> 27:00.970
the darkest

27:00.970 --> 27:03.710
time that we are experiencing

27:03.710 --> 27:05.710
in Afghanistan. The number

27:05.710 --> 27:07.590
that the Taliban

27:07.590 --> 27:09.230
are trying to

27:09.930 --> 27:11.230
