27:11.230 --> 27:13.230
is very different what we

27:14.190 --> 27:15.190
have receiving

27:15.190 --> 27:17.630
from the people. I think

27:17.630 --> 27:19.150
in that area

27:19.150 --> 27:21.310
we have, we had

27:21.310 --> 27:23.270
more than 20

27:23.270 --> 27:25.250
violets which are

27:25.250 --> 27:26.730
completely destroyed

27:28.170 --> 27:29.610
in the

27:30.090 --> 27:30.990
earthquake.

27:31.710 --> 27:33.330
And also there

27:33.330 --> 27:35.330
is no way for the

27:35.330 --> 27:36.910
actually in the first hour

27:36.910 --> 27:39.270
the Taliban tried to control the medias.

27:39.830 --> 27:41.370
We didn't receive the

27:41.370 --> 27:43.230
actually we thought that everything

27:43.230 --> 27:45.010
is not that

27:45.010 --> 27:47.190
bad what

27:48.210 --> 27:48.810
we

27:48.810 --> 27:51.370
when we

27:51.370 --> 27:53.630
sent the volunteers

27:53.630 --> 27:55.070
group to the area.

27:56.710 --> 27:57.310
Actually

27:57.310 --> 27:58.310
I'm so sorry.

27:59.190 --> 28:01.490
No, don't worry. And so Angela, basically

28:01.490 --> 28:03.430
the Taliban have gone

28:03.430 --> 28:05.410
back to what they said. The numbers have changed.

28:05.590 --> 28:07.170
But what are people saying

28:07.170 --> 28:09.390
on the ground, those who have been affected?

28:11.590 --> 28:12.790
They don't

28:12.790 --> 28:15.030
accept the numbers which

28:15.030 --> 28:16.530
the Taliban is shedding.

28:17.370 --> 28:19.270
Actually, and also

28:19.830 --> 28:21.130
I think more

28:21.130 --> 28:23.510
than 2,000 people are killed.

28:24.210 --> 28:25.350
A thousand people

28:25.350 --> 28:26.250
displaced.

28:27.430 --> 28:28.930
A thousand people are

28:28.930 --> 28:31.010
missing in this

28:31.010 --> 28:32.410
crisis.

28:33.330 --> 28:35.270
And we have

28:35.270 --> 28:36.930
nothing at that moment.

28:37.370 --> 28:39.270
At this moment there are

28:39.270 --> 28:40.990
no big

28:40.990 --> 28:43.210
offer or support from

